              <li>cGMP Regulations</li>
              <li>OEB Best Practices</li>
              <li>ISO 14644-1/2 (Cleanrooms)</li>
              <li>AIHA Laboratory Accreditation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-primaryBlue mb-2 text-xl font-semibold">Applications & Industries</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray list-inside list-disc">
              <li>Pharmaceutical Manufacturing</li>
              <li>Biotechnology</li>
              <li>Contract Research Organizations</li>
              <li>HPAPI Processing</li>
              <li>Containment Facility Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Conclusion -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-primaryBlue mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold">Why Partner with Us?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Our CRO delivers expert isolator containment validation to ensure your pharmaceutical operations are safe,
          compliant, and efficient. With Certified Industrial Hygienists, AIHA-accredited lab partnerships, and
          adherence to ISPE SMEPAC and cGMP standards, we provide reliable solutions for handling potent compounds.
          Choose us to safeguard your workforce, protect the environment, and streamline your regulatory compliance.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <div class="bg-secondary-light border-secondary mb-12 border p-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold">Ready to Ensure Safe Handling of Potent Compounds?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray mb-4">Partner with us for expert isolator validation and compliance solutions.</p>
      <BTN btnLink="/contact-us" btnClass="button" btnText="Contact Us Today" />
    </div>

    <section class="maxwidth">
      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <Faq faqs={mainEntity} />
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
